drawings.author: ZWZhNTMzZTE2NzI3
drawings.text: Based on instructions, certain characters, if not dead, could be in multiple spots on the map. They are placed here with relevant commentary.

drawings.author: ZWZhNTMzZTE2NzI3
drawings.text: Noska Ur'gray is in X28 if he is not with Xanathar in X6

drawings.author: ZWZhNTMzZTE2NzI3
drawings.text: Xanathar's location:  Roll 1d100. 01-50, Xanathar is talking to Sylgar, its pet fish in area X19. On a 51-75, Xanathar is delivering a rambling sermon to minions in the audience chamber (area X18). On a 76-90, Xanathar is watching a fight in the Pit of Blood and Fortune (area X6). On a 91-100, Xanathar is contemplating its mortality in the crypt, amid the remains of past xanathars (area X33)

drawings.author: ZWZhNTMzZTE2NzI3
drawings.text: When they're not watching a tournament in the arena (area X6) or listening to Xanathar give a speech in the audience chamber (area X18), ten human bandits are in area X9

drawings.author: ZWZhNTMzZTE2NzI3
drawings.text: If he is not with Xanathar in the arena (Area X6), Ahmaergo is conducting a routine inspection of the dungeon in X17. If he sees intruders and is outnumbered, Ahmaergo retreats to area X22, heads downstairs to gather reingorcements from area X28.
